<!-- Button trigger modal -->
<button type="button" class="btn mr-1 px-2 py-1" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#spazerBeforePlasmaModal">
<i class="bi bi-question-circle"></i>
</button>

<!-- Modal -->
<div class="modal" id="spazerBeforePlasmaModal" tabindex="-1">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h1 class="modal-title fs-5">Spazer before Plasma</h1>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>If enabled, Spazer will be prioritized before Plasma both as a key item and as filler (if applicable). This makes 
        it more likely that Spazer would be obtainable before Plasma. It could still happen that both beams are placed on the 
        same step, or that Plasma is placed first if it would provide progression when Spazer would not.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>




